Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:44.99,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}本字幕由极影字幕社制作 仅供交流试看 喜爱本作品的请支持Z版
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:44.99,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻译:无明拂晓  校译:dente翼 时间:MACO 特效：MACO 后期:纱布君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.78,0:01:13.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}すぐに　すぐに　すぐに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.78,0:01:13.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即 立即 立即
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.15,0:01:15.93,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}やみを越え　駆けつける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.15,0:01:15.93,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越黑暗 飞奔而来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.30,0:01:21.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大切な人を守りぬきたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.30,0:01:21.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要一直守护心爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.33,0:01:34.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}そのとき　歯車は　まわりだしてた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.33,0:01:34.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候 齿轮开始转动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.38,0:01:47.33,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}運命導くよ　君のもとへと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.38,0:01:47.33,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运引导我 来到你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.80,0:01:53.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}芽生えた思い　隠していても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.80,0:01:53.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌生的爱恋 无法遮掩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:02:01.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}瞳を見れば　気持ちは揺れるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:02:01.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着你的眼睛 心情就会动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:06.89,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}願うことは一つ　壊れないこの心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:06.89,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个愿望 希望有颗坚强的心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:12.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}どんな試練に倒れるとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:12.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论在多么残酷的考验中倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:15.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}すぐに　すぐに　すぐに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:15.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即 立即 立即
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:18.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}もう一度　立ち上がる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:18.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会再站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.81,0:02:21.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}そう　君よ　どうか待ってて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.81,0:02:21.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 请你等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.79,0:02:24.85,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}弱さ断ち切るのは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.79,0:02:24.85,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我战胜软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.17,0:02:27.61,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}君がくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.17,0:02:27.61,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.95,0:02:31.64,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}justice of light
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.95,0:02:31.64,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,justice of light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.88,0:00:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次见到的天空 是血色的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.71,0:00:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次闻到的气味 是血腥味
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.54,0:00:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人 被杀的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远不会醒来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.39,0:00:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.09,0:00:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何不让我安眠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.14,0:00:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何我得不到救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.13,0:00:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.75,0:00:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的人都饥饿难忍像猪一样狼吞虎咽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.26,0:01:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 随你便
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.59,0:01:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么……只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.01,0:02:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第3话 魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阿莉亚 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是塞希莉·坎贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.52,0:03:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的任务就拜托你了 塞希莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 那么 我要保护的物品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.34,0:03:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汉尼巴尔 你还没说明给她听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因为这样比较有意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.39,0:03:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低级趣味啊 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要保护的就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保护的不是魔剑么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢 又有什么事让你跑到我家来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路克 真遗憾 今天不是来找你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.81,0:03:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也不遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑开过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟笨蛋骑士 日常对话都没法沟通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会砍了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.43,0:03:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.16,0:03:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 他们俩是恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你差点毁了我的清誉 快点否认
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.03,0:04:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到这副情景 还有谁认为我们是恋人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒真想见见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.54,0:04:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（快点否认）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（放手）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（闭嘴 快点）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 含有的灵体很丰富啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的 我在里面加入了从灰森林采来的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这附近灵体度真高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们来说真是值得庆幸的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人怎么会是魔剑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.73,0:04:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 问得好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能麻烦你一下嘛 阿莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除睡眠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住真相
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风在手中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.21,0:05:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以弑神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她变成剑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.52,0:05:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是剑变成人了 这真少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是魔剑阿莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是人也是剑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.63,0:05:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔剑会产生风
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的风 不是使用祈祷契约产生的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.92,0:06:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 要使用祈祷契约 是需要玉刚作为催化剂的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那个反应不是玉刚做成的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.14,0:06:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害 这样就好说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能产生风 寄宿着未知的力量 真是魔剑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉亚 可以了 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 魔剑是各国都觊觎的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.33,0:06:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然让你保护
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不会想到魔剑会以人的样子走在街上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 护卫越少越好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样身为女孩的我更方便嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是说出去了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.97,0:07:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会那样做的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.51,0:07:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天来干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.67,0:07:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点事想请莉莎帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.88,0:07:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人肯定会再次对准魔剑来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 很有可能在市内执行恶魔契约
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 肯定又要有人牺牲了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们早就做好了心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.90,0:07:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们记住一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要畏惧死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.89,0:07:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管如此 还要勇敢面对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这将成为你们和恶魔战斗时最强的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.29,0:07:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们眼前的老头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.19,0:07:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样在上次的战争中存活下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 下面决定警卫的部署
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团长 在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么让塞希莉·坎贝尔保护魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是坎贝尔家族的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 一定会不负希望的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吃点 多喝点 不要客气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.89,0:08:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉串太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来3人份烤肉串 还有白薯丸子和蜂蜜果子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.82,0:08:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加3人份烤肉串
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 连我的也……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀 所有费用都能报销的 不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:08:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 是我说想要尽情地边吃边逛的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:09:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说如此 但我对这种事不是很在行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莎能跟我们一起真是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.65,0:09:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这家店真是来对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,量足又好吃 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊 我也一直好想来这里吃一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉串太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃得太快会噎着的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 那个没出息的人都不请你吃东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 路克下个星期会去市集吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.05,0:09:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 路克也会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那莉莎也很期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 虽然每次都去市集 但都不是去玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.37,0:09:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路克一直在找一样东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.98,0:09:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 能杀死神的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.28,0:10:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我什么都没说 没说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.34,0:10:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神……神……杀……不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能对付他的 很厉害的剑……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能有的话就……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好吃 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来点芋头丸子 还有鸡肉鸡蛋汤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风之魔剑 阿莉亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.47,0:10:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以弑神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能……那个女人是……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.87,0:10:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 算了 人各有命 剑也如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 来点茶……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.82,0:10:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:11:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个城市真不错啊 治安很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好的是 没有死的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.90,0:11:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的了 城市里怎么会有那种味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.15,0:11:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有那样的城市哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸体横遍的大路 也并不少见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从以前就经很多人之手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.65,0:11:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢姐姐 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.32,0:11:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉亚 你多大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.30,0:11:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,40到50之间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,40……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多这个年纪吧 我醒来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:12:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正值恶魔战争 就在战场之中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.57,0:12:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然以剑的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.98,0:12:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在那里 是谁把我带到那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是风之魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.22,0:12:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道这个的人们 眼神顿变 相互争夺起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.41,0:12:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像野兽一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多人死了 死在我这把剑下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.57,0:12:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真残酷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以夺取人性命开始 之后一直杀戮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.95,0:13:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不……是在被迫杀戮的啊 阿莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔剑到底是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道 但是一定是伤害人的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.75,0:13:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是剑 是魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 本来不是要说这些的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 就是这个城市很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.81,0:13:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是塞希莉你们尽职守护的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.63,0:13:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话 真想一直待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请一定留下来 我一定会保护阿莉亚的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 请一直留在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.17,0:14:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你的东西...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.06,0:14:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比普通的剑要小一圈 我想应该比较好用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.52,0:14:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罕见的形状呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.27,0:14:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(注释：force edge：“力量之刃”斯巴达剑) 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.27,0:14:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是force edge吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是莉莎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.50,0:14:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅仅能斩切 也很适合刺和戳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前 先好好学会斩切如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.06,0:14:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,列吉拉鲁德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴蒂 我的剑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.90,0:14:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没本事的话 有宝物也不会用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.49,0:15:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为如此 才依赖精巧的武器的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个失礼的男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.93,0:15:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是口无遮拦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用 Zweihander
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（注释：Zweihander：德国双手剑。长过6英尺2英寸的巨大武器）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.73,0:15:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑是杀人的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把眼前的敌人击倒 除此之外没有任何意义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并……并不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑士的剑是为了保护市民而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑就是剑 只是武器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这样的男人 我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.78,0:15:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去砍别人刺别人 夺取别人的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.70,0:15:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为剑这样使用就行了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了 因心中充满绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.96,0:16:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二小队去东区 第四小队去西区
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.99,0:16:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现了黑衣男子 绝对不能让他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.36,0:16:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等等 团长 我也要出动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 你留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.29,0:16:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 只有我在安全的地方待命这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.09,0:16:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的任务是保护魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团长 那究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次的战争中使用的一种特殊的虫类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.44,0:17:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它进入了人的体内的话 就会侵入大脑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人就会变成被它操纵的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个都不能留下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囚犯全体都误吞下虫……这样说不通呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.73,0:17:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣男子...吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.95,0:18:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞希莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没关系的 我当然明白自己的任务是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.14,0:18:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的哦 塞希莉的任务是保护这个城市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对我说的 一直待在这里也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在塞希莉你们守卫着的 这座没有死亡气味的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别大意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.74,0:18:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 黑衣男子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家退后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.81,0:19:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.35,0:19:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被虫控制了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行尸走肉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被虫... 那他也是受害者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.73,0:19:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也能这么说...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.52,0:19:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有办法救他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 变成那样的话 除了杀了他别无他法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.88,0:20:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要怕啊 塞希莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么 塞希莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.08,0:20:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞希莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 危险
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.92,0:20:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路克
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞希莉 快杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是人 是人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 我凭什么剥夺他的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.95,0:20:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你……从没杀过人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.94,0:20:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么 塞希莉·坎贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.73,0:20:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快挥剑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个胆小鬼 别做骑士了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.30,0:21:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞希莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.30,0:21:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我……一点都没变
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自认为成长一些可以战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.53,0:21:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞希莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个让人没办法的老好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还真不知道 竟有这么害怕杀人的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定会长寿的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.27,0:21:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.18,0:21:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么我得不到救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.71,0:21:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和恶魔缔结下契约
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那场战争中存活了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牺牲自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:21:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以让我来给你救赎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.49,0:21:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.11,0:22:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在找像你这样的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.87,0:22:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地狱中存活下来 却逃不出地狱的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.43,0:22:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就由我来拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.74,0:22:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的灵魂来交换
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:41.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}そっと　そっと　そばにいます
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:41.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻轻地 静静地 在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.94,0:22:44.38,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}そよ風のように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.94,0:22:44.38,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如微风一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.31,0:22:48.70,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}しゅんとする涙なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.31,0:22:48.70,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻轻吹干
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.03,0:22:51.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}かわかせるように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.03,0:22:51.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.20,0:22:58.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ポケットの中の 小さなねがいは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.20,0:22:58.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口袋中的 小小愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.78,0:23:05.07,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}あなたの笑顔だから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.78,0:23:05.07,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你的笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:09.90,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}走れ　走れ　もっとはやく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:09.90,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奔跑吧 再快些
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.22,0:23:13.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}悲しいことあった時も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.22,0:23:13.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤心的时候也要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.86,0:23:16.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}かけてゆこう　この道を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.86,0:23:16.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿着这条路跑下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.29,0:23:22.11,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}地図なんていつも心にある
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.29,0:23:22.11,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地图一直永远在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.43,0:23:25.53,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}明日はhappy day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.43,0:23:25.53,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是快乐的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:33.01,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ちらり みらくるhappy day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:33.01,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪耀奇迹的快乐一天
